data.description:
The perfect location! *Buyer will pay NO RE TAXES through the remainder of the year as the owner has tax exemption in place on the property.  This is a beautiful 4/2 well kept home on a cul de sac. Like-new ranch style home is located close to everything! The beach, Mayport Naval Station, schools and shopping are all just a few minutes from this location. Split - open floor plan with luxury vinyl plank flooring (no carpet!), kitchen granite countertops, quartz in the bathrooms, and home is wrapped in Hardee-lap siding. Spacious kitchen with 42'' cabinets and soft-close drawers. Large fully fenced back yard, sprinkler system, has  raised garden beds in the back yard (already planted full of vegetables), and water softener system. You will love this property - won't last long! A beautiful home for your family! Seller will pay up to 5K of closing costs.
*Raised garden beds in the backyard are optional. Buyer can keep or they will be removed. No extra charges to keep the beds.
